    "As presented in Table 2, the average accuracy for both AP-On and AP-Off conditions was recorded at 100% for all participants, irrespective of the training methods.",
    "However, the lower deviation and shorter response times of the ChatGPT groups suggest a better learning outcome of this approach.",
    "A statistical comparison between the groups, employing the Mann-Whitney U test, was conducted for both AP-On and AP-Off conditions."
